description._content: 1500+ attendees joined us for the 7th edition of TEDxHyderabad on September 18th! A day filled with so many memories and grateful to see Ideas from the stage evolving into massive social impact in the city and beyond over the past 7 years! An important milestone in our journey of building a community of Thinkers, Enablers and Doers - One Idea at a time! We had 13 inspiring speakers and 9 standing ovations. The theme was #Rising! #TEDxHyderabad #7th
